{"tid":322280,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[撳吓掣就投到]LIHKG香港超級女神聯賽亞洲挑戰盃泰國站初賽日","createTime":"2017-07-14T16:29:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-15T21:38:20.000Z","uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"167072ae7fe504279f94ad242e8eef172bb93d09","tid":322280,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:29:30.000Z","msg":"以下為即將舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可留意稍後時間發出的比賽專用回覆並以回覆評分功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(唔識點樣用回覆評分功能黎投票既巴打可以參考下面既教學)<br />\n<br />\n12:30am Peechaya Wattanamontree vs 倪晨曦<br />\n12:32am 李靜儀@SG vs 馮盈盈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hiNda68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhiNda68.png&h=d4221617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s2sfX8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs2sfX8L.png&h=b53ffa65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"82a32a0dc00287a196ff053d730e1d640c4d776b","tid":322280,"uid":92376,"like":7,"dislike":20,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:30:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">LIHKG香港超級女神聯賽亞洲挑戰盃泰國站</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">初賽日</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-7-15 12:30am-10:30pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/uSPJUxC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FuSPJUxC.png&h=8ffd3c0b&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/reyTtq5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FreyTtq5.png&h=52b7ec3f&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/qdKYOI7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqdKYOI7.png&h=8719e985&s={SIZE}\" />Peechaya Wattanamontree vs 倪晨曦</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">賽事時限為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">友誼賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"11099caa2546385c830496537e7a0b1a5f2a489e","tid":322280,"uid":92376,"like":21,"dislike":12,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:32:03.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">初賽日</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-7-15 12:32am-10:32pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/clu1GSf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fclu1GSf.png&h=fe7c2b0d&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/90BwhA3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F90BwhA3.png&h=e79a77ae&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">李靜儀@SG vs 馮盈盈</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">賽事時限為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">友誼賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"d8cf1a1c03890adaac76012e0d7ef61d8f101a34","tid":322280,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:36:42.000Z","msg":"有野講講<br />\n其實投票，唔一定每種投票既性質都係要大家識或者鍾意果一個人先至可以投票<br />\n大家可以憑住審美眼光黎投票，決定邊個好啲靚啲咪投邊個，選美評審都唔會知道面前既女仔係咩人，只係客觀選擇<br />\n巴打們不妨可以抱住呢個心態黎參與我地既活動呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c01454a2a928743e805162484455a4c8f3c49357","tid":322280,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:42:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\